Assignment 0

Installation Steps and Issues:
1. Download mpich-3.2.1 tar file
2. tar xfz mpich-3.2.1.tar.gz
3. mkdir install directory
4. ./configure --disable-fortran -prefix=/home/light/6th-Sem/CS633/mpich_install |& tee c.txt
	-> --disable-fortran : flag for disabling the need for Fortran compiler since I’m not going to code in fortran

5. make 2>&1 | tee m.txt
6. make install |& tee mi.txt
7. Use this command to check the local installation: mpiexec -n 4 ./examples/cpi
8. This completes the actual execution and we can now compress the install directory and the actual mpich-3.2.1 directory and copy them to one of the lab machines. SSH into one of the machines and set up Passwordless-SSH with another machine on the cluster, this will automatically set it up with all machines in the cluster.
	-> Easiest way to enable passwordless-ssh
	-> Don’t put passphrase on your ssh-keys when you generate them afresh.
9. export PATH=/users/misc/raditya/6th-Sem/CS633/mpich_install/bin:$PATH

